body:
@jreback maybe some docs are indeed enough for what I was looking for, as I was not fully aware that the Categorical already existed (I just thought it was some experimental feature that was not further developed, as there is exactly zero documentation about this).

On the other hand, if we want to make some changes to the API, it is now the moment when making it a first class citizen and adding documentation.

It was also because I saw quite some discussion about the API (naming for levels/labels/values/pointers/..., how they should behave in certain operations, .. in the discussion in this PR and #6242), that I thought this should require a broader discussion.
